title: WinPE8.0 (x86/Native x86) WinPE10 Sergei Strelec (x64)
description:
WinPE8.0 (x86/Native x86) WinPE10 Sergei Strelec (x64)

About this release

Purpose: computer maintenance, hard disks and partitions management, backup and restore disks and partitions, computer diagnostics, data recovery, Windows installation.
Release date: 7/6/2016
Language: english
Usage: burn ISO to USB using included Rufus 2.9
Author / Credits: Sergei Strelec http://sergeistrelec.ru/

About WinPE8.0 (x86/Native x86) WinPE10 Sergei Strelec (x64)

This bootable iso offers a huge collection of utilities for Windows systems (Windows and DOS applications, Network utilities, Drivers).
The x86 version is based on WinPE8 (for older computers), the x64 version is based on WinPE10.

Network
Supported methods and protocols: TCP/IP, NetBIOS, PPPoE, and WLAN (Wi-Fi).
If you want use Wi-Fi - you need to install "wireless network-adapter driver". Choose "Drivers" section in the "Start Menu".
Connecting to Wi-Fi require to use "PE Network Manger", click on tab "Wi-Fi" on it.

Drivers
You can put your WLAN or controller driver in the "SSTRUSERMY_DRIVERS_x64" or "SSTRUSERMY_DRIVERS_x86" folder
Driver will be installed while Windows PE is booting.
